title: Crossroads at Elm Creek - Just the place you're looking for!
posting_body: ['Crossroads at Elm Creek - A place to call home!', 'Bed: 3 / Bath: 2', 'Sq.', 'Footage: 1481 sq ft', 'Rent: $2407 - $2602/Month', 'Terms: 6-Month, 9-Month, 12-Month, 15-Month, 18-Month', 'show contact info', 'It is possible to have it all - modern style and comfort.', 'An exceptional kitchen space connects to your living area where upscale finishes add a level of warmth that makes your home a place to celebrate the everyday.', "Plus, when you are ready to set foot outside your front door, you'll be rewarded with a suite of retreat-worthy amenities like a clubhouse and a swimming pool.", 'Our Apartment Homes Feature:', '❖ Cable Ready', '❖ Ceiling Fan', '❖ Dishwasher', '❖ Large Windows in Every Room', '❖ Private Balconies or Patios In Most Units', '❖ Range', '❖ Refrigerator', '❖ Stainless Steel Appliances', '❖ Storage Units', '❖ Vinyl Wood Plank Flooring', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '❖ 24-Hour Fitness Center', '❖ BBQ/Picnic Area', '❖ Beautiful Pergola-Covered Seating and Grilling Area', '❖ Game Room', '❖ On-Site Management', '❖ Package Receiving', '❖ Playground', '❖ Professionally Designed and Maintained Landscape', '❖ Recycling', '❖ Smoke-Free Campus', '❖ 24-Hour Fitness Center', '❖ Beautiful Pergola-Covered Seating and Grilling Area', "❖ Children's Play Area with Large Playground Equipment", '❖ Community-Wide WiFi', '❖ High-Speed Internet', '❖ On-Site Maintenance', '❖ Planned Social Activities', '❖ Professionally Designed and Maintained Landscape', '❖ Renters Liability Program', '❖ Resident Services Portal with Online Payment & Maintenance Request Options', 'Contact Info:', 'show contact info', '14151 Territorial Rd', 'Maple Grove, MN 55369', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Pets:', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Non-aggressive breeds accepted.', 'Weight Restrictions may apply.', 'Please see the office for fees & other details!', 'Prices are subject to change.', 'Contact Leasing for details!', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'AEFFD440997749D']
